<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Flowering" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Flowering,</orth> 1) blooming: <cit><quote>f. infants,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.14" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 14</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>all my f. youth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.56" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 56</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) covered with flowers: <cit><quote>the snake rolled in a f. bank,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.228" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 228</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O serpent heart, hid with a f. face,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 73</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>